1. *On* je odgovoran za svoja dela. (He is responsible for his actions.)
2. On je bio *odgovoran* za svoje reči. (He was responsible for his words.)
3. U njemu je izraženo *odgovorno* ponašanje. (Responsible behavior was expressed in him.)
4. *Odgovornost* je njegov najveći kvalitet. (Responsibility is his greatest quality.)
5. On je veoma *odgovoran* na poslu. (He is very responsible at work.)